headline: MOTORTREND NAMES MERCEDES-BENZ E-CLASS 2025 CAR OF THE YEAR
summary: MotorTrend Group, a Warner Bros. Discovery company, announced today the Mercedes-Benz E-Class as its 2025 Car of the Year award winner. The new E-Class, available as both a sedan and wagon-crossover, claimed the top spot amongst competitors for its elegant, refreshed design, excellent performance, and technology.
